<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <%- include('partials/head') %>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/axios/dist/axios.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.9.1/gsap.min.js"></script>

    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f9fafb;
        color: #1f2937;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      .main-content {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding-left: 8rem;
        padding-right: 8rem;
        padding-top: 5rem;
        padding-bottom: 5rem;
      }

      .dark-mode .main-content {
        background-color: #1c2535;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
      }

      .title-section {
        text-align: left;
      }

      .title-section h1 {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 2.4rem;
        color: #2563eb;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }

      .dark-mode .title-section h1 {
        color: #3b82f6;
      }

      .title-section p {
        color: #555;
        max-width: 700px;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        text-align: left;
      }

      .dark-mode .title-section p {
        color: #d1d5db;
      }

      section {
        margin: 2rem 0;
      }

      section h2 {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
        color: #333;
        display: flex;
        align-items: start;
        border-left: 4px solid #2563eb;
        padding-left: 8px;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }

      .dark-mode section h2 {
        color: #e5e7eb;
        border-left-color: #3b82f6;
      }

      section h2 i {
        margin-right: 8px;
        color: #6f42c1;
      }

      .sidebar {
        width: 25%;
        background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #007bff, #6f42c1);
        color: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
        position: sticky;
        top: 0;
        height: calc(100vh - 40px);
        box-shadow: 2px 0 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }

      .dark-mode .sidebar {
        background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #1a1b4e, #1f1f1f);
      }

      .sidebar ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
      }

      .sidebar ul li {
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }

      .sidebar ul li a {
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 1rem;
        display: flex;
        align-items: start;
        padding: 8px;
        transition: color 0.2s;
        border-radius: 4px;
      }

      .sidebar ul li a:hover {
        color: #e0e0e0;
      }

      .dark-mode .sidebar ul li a:hover {
        color: #ffffff;
      }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .main-content {
          width: 100%;
          padding: 1rem;
        }

        .sidebar {
          display: none;
        }
      }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

  <%- include('partials/navbar') %>
    <main class="main-content">
      <div class="title-section">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <div>
          <h2>Our Mission</h2>
          <p>At <%= appName %>, we believe in fostering strong local connections and promoting sustainable,
              community-driven commerce. Our platform is built to make buying and selling easier, safer, and more
              accessible for everyone.</p>
        </div>
        <h2>What We Offer</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Buy & Sell Locally: Find great deals on items you need or sell your own goods easily.</li>
          <li>Trusted Listings: All our listings are community-driven, allowing for safe exchanges.</li>
          <li>Community Focused: We're here to support local businesses and promote neighborhood connections.</li>
        </ul>
        <div>
          <h2>How It Works</h2>
          <p>Simply create a free account, post your ads, browse listings, and connect with others in your community.
            From finding food to housing, <%= appName %> brings your local market online.</p>
        </div>
        <h2>Our Values</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Trust</li>
          <li>Community</li>
          <li>Convenience</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Thank you for choosing <%= appName %>â€”where local communities come together!</p>
      </div>
    </main>

</body>
<%- include('partials/footer') %>

</html>